2. PRODUCT / PROTOTYPE CONTEXT
====================================================================

This prototype represents the NFI Beneficiary Management System (NFI BMS), previously referred to as NFI CMDWS.

The final approved prototype will be treated as the source of truth for the development team.

The current work is still prototype/UI-focused.
The March 18 discussion clarified that the next revision should remain UI-first and should not silently lock in backend or workflow changes unless explicitly agreed.

Primary project goal:
Create an MVP system to manage neonatal support cases end-to-end, including:
- intake
- documents
- validation
- review / approvals
- post-discharge / settlement
- volunteer follow-up
- reporting

Current architecture direction in project documents:
- Angular UI -> Spring Boot APIs -> MySQL + Blob/S3-style storage
However, the current UI prototype codebase being iterated is the existing prototype implementation and should be modified in-place, not rebuilt from scratch.

