B. IMPORTANT MARCH 18 SCOPE BOUNDARIES
These must be respected in V3.5:
- NO in-app video / MP4 upload support
- NO mandatory discharge photo/video support unless separately approved
- NO multilingual digital consent interaction inside the app
- consent should be treated as an uploaded signed document
- underage validation should BLOCK SUBMIT, not auto-reject in workflow
- panel direction should preserve the current flow as much as possible
- prototype round should remain primarily UI-focused

